  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>. This  A-class fighter benefits from damage and maneuverability bonuses, and is pre-installed with a selection of technologies and upgrades.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>。这艘A级战斗机拥有伤害与机动力加成，除此以外还预装有一系列技术与升级。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>。這艘 A 級戰鬥機配備精選科技與升級設備，有傷害和機動力加成。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>太空船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
